OL,5, The Body Shop's UK business is set to  
OL,6, appoint administrators this week, in a 
OL,7, move likely to result in shop closures 
OL,8, and job losses.                        
OL,10,FThe owner of the company, set up in    
OL,11,F1976 by the late Dame Anita Roddick, is
OL,12,Fexpected to appoint experts to         
OL,13,Fsignificantly restructure the retailer.
OL,15,FThe Body Shop was bought by private    
OL,16,Fequity firm Aurelius just weeks ago.   
OL,18,FIt is understood that trading over the 
OL,19,Fkey Christmas period and into January  
OL,20,Fwas not as strong as hoped.            
